// INSTALL for the Card Game Engine 

To setup CGE server:
- install and set up WordPress (can rename "wordpress" dir to "cards" or such)
- create WP user for each player
- create a directory for the game engine under the wordpress plugin directory
- initialize git in game engine subdirectory
- pull down code from the git repository into game engine subdir
- in WP, create a new page and add the tag "[cge_launch_link]"
